ey attacked him, and a way to free himself from the curse. He now spends his time as a caravan guard, hoping to learn what he can from merchants as he travels. All he knows is the name Eaters of the Lotus, and little more.</p><p>His wife (Aurelia) died shortly after the birth of their daughter (Videlea, 18).<br>Heard word he now has a son-in-law (Oryzan, 18) before being dispatched, but has not met the man.</p><p>Name meaning<br>Sextus / Marcus: Common roman first names<br>Pontifus: Pontificate, talks a lot<br>Gloriator: braggart<br>Herculeus: Hercules (duh), as he thinks he is still strong<br>Satanus: Adversary, picked as he fights against himself and the curse<br>Videlae: Videl (Hercule's daughter in DBZ)<br>Oryzan: Latin for Rice (Gohan means \\"cooked rice\\" in Japanese)</p>", "Hair Color": "Black", "Style of Dress": "Ancient Soldier / Commoner", "Melodramatic Hook": "Attacked by a group he learned was the Eaters of the Lotus, who were after the sword he found and picked up.\\nThe sword is cursed, driving the wielder to bloodlust.\\nHe hopes to someday find the origin of the curse, and to break the curse, not just upon himself, but upon the sword.\\nHe refuses to let any carry it, or touch it, for fear the curse will afflict them.\\nHopes to someday redeem himself for his crime of killing his own men. Until that day, he will not return home to Constantinople, or his family."}	{"Will": 0, "Deceit": 0, "Fix-It": 0, "Notice": 0, "Police": 0, "Driving": 0, "Gambling": 11, "Medicine": 0, "Sabotage": 0, "Strength": 0, "Detective": 0, "Intrusion": 13, "Seduction": 0, "Leadership": 0, "Constituion": 0, "Intimidation": 0, "Info: Smithing & Metallurgy": 14}	830d358c-789e-4e98-b511-753a0aa8d410	\N	f	236e0b55-d417-80e7-9cb4-d800d6a9b7d8	2025-07-20 19:13:38.198557	\N	\N	\N	\N
