ener noreferrer\\" data-mention-id=\\"0efadcdd-58c6-4844-91a7-2a0527b305a2\\" data-mention-class-name=\\"Faction\\">@The Ascended</a> in charge of the drug runners, too. Having traveled with the Dragons for some time now, Penny has come to the conclusion that she cannot put an end to the chi war. However, she wants to aid their goals and help the Dragons to claim the modern juncture, or at least to loosen the grip the Ascended have upon it. After the loss of <a href=\\"/characters/8b484001-0278-4af1-9dd6-137d0ed12c7d\\" class=\\"mention\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener noreferrer\\" data-mention-id=\\"8b484001-0278-4af1-9dd6-137d0ed12c7d\\" data-mention-class-name=\\"Character\\">@Serena Tessaro</a>, she wants to create the magical tome to replace the one lost to honor her friend and fellow mage, the Tessaro Infernum. To that end... she has no idea where to start yet. But she knows she'll need magical artifacts, and maybe more power. Helping to solve this issue with Manly International may lead her to that conclusion.</p>"}	{"Will": 0, "Deceit": 0, "Fix-It": 0, "Notice": 0, "Police": 12, "Driving": 0, "Gambling": 0, "Medicine": 0, "Sabotage": 0, "Strength": 0, "Detective": 0, "Intrusion": 0, "Seduction": 0, "Leadership": 0, "Constituion": 0, "Info: Occult": 13, "Intimidation": 0}	830d358c-789e-4e98-b511-753a0aa8d410	https://ik.imagekit.io/nvqgwnjgv/chi-war-production/penelope_98vBXG35q.png	\N	c9d8393d-011a-4ac6-b436-c35cf14f3f4a	\N	\N	5c7d5473-9d5a-4539-b38a-39bd1a2393e4	Working Stiff	\N
