"Cinder" Jackson	\N	\N	2024-03-14 01:09:20.591514	2025-07-20 12:46:45.934584		4f7a222f-e07f-480f-9e21-6df53c0c59ff	{"Guns": 15, "Type": "Ally", "Speed": 7, "Damage": 9, "Genome": 0, "Mutant": 0, "Wounds": 0, "Defense": 13, "Fortune": 0, "Sorcery": 0, "Creature": 0, "Archetype": "", "Toughness": 7, "MainAttack": "Guns", "FortuneType": "Fortune", "Max Fortune": 0, "Martial Arts": 0, "Scroungetech": 0, "Marks of Death": 0, "SecondaryAttack": "Martial Arts"}	721d930b-9a16-4fd2-8410-b9d47906c59a	0f2b51c0-80c0-4f5f-b55f-76186903df3e	t	{"Age": "24", "Height": "5''3\\"", "Weight": "112 lbs", "Eye Color": "hazel", "Nicknames": "", "Appearance": "<p>Driver for the <a href=\\"/factions/3d424d4e-ca38-4a06-a28d-7d0ccb1f44cf\\" class=\\"Editor_mention__L81up\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener noreferrer\\" data-mention-id=\\"3d424d4e-ca38-4a06-a28d-7d0ccb1f44cf\\" data-mention-class-name=\\"Faction\\">@Runnerpunks</a> in the Cyberpunk Future.</p>", "Background": "<p>Cinder Jackson is a skilled driver with lightning-fast reflexes and nerves of steel, essential traits for navigating the chaotic streets of cyberpunk San Angeles . Her appearance reflects the gritty aesthetic of the Runnerpunks —sporting multiple neon-colored tattoos that glow faintly against her dark skin. Her hair is styled in a vibrant undercut, with one side shaved and decorated with circuit-pattern tattoos, while the other side falls in bright copper-colored dreadlocks accented with metallic threads that catch the light when she moves.</p><p>Despite her relatively small frame, Cinder's presence is commanding. She moves with the practiced efficiency of someone who has spent years behind the wheel in high-pressure situations. Her eyes, enhanced with subtle cybernetic implants that give her superior night vision and targeting assistance, scan her surroundings constantly—a habit developed from years of evading Manlysaka patrols.</p><p>She typically wears reinforced leather racing gear adorned with the Runnerpunks' insignia, fingerless gloves that allow her better tactile feedback when driving, and heavy boots with hidden compartments for emergency tools and weapons.</p><h2>Role and Position</h2><p>As the primary driver for the Runnerpunks, Cinder Jackson is responsible for all major transportation operations—from high-speed extractions to supply runs through hostile territory. Her exceptional skill behind the wheel has earned her a respected position within the group's hierarchy, just below \\"Scorch\\" O'Connor 's leadership circle.</p><p>Cinder maintains and modifies the Runnerpunks' fleet of vehicles, including the armored jalopy she drives during critical missions. Her mechanical aptitude complements her driving skills, allowing her to make split-second repairs even in the midst of a chase.</p><p>Her relationship with other Runnerpunks is particularly notable with Luis Ortega, the cyberbrute whose sacrifice during the Manly-Saka extraction mission visibly affected her. Her anguished cry of \\"No, Luis!\\" when his fate was uncertain suggests a deep personal connection between them.</p><h2>Combat Capability</h2><p>Though primarily valued for her driving abilities, Cinder is no stranger to combat. During the extraction of Doctor Cyborg, she demonstrated proficiency with firearms, providing covering fire for her teammates when necessary. Her tactical driving maneuvers serve as both offense and defense, using her vehicle as a weapon when the situation demands it.</p><h2>Personality</h2><p>Fiercely loyal to the Runnerpunks' cause, Cinder maintains a tough exterior that occasionally cracks to reveal deep emotional connections with her comrades. She's quick-thinking under pressure and willing to take calculated risks to complete a mission. Her reaction to witnessing Penelope Andrews‘ magical abilities—staring in shock—hints at a practical worldview shaped by the technological dystopia she calls home, where magic remains an anomaly.</p>", "Hair Color": "black", "Style of Dress": "Tough, combat-ready", "Melodramatic Hook": ""}	{"Will": 0, "Deceit": 0, "Fix-It": 0, "Notice": 0, "Police": 0, "Driving": 13, "Gambling": 0, "Medicine": 0, "Sabotage": 0, "Strength": 0, "Detective": 0, "Intrusion": 0, "Seduction": 0, "Leadership": 0, "Constituion": 0, "Intimidation": 0}	3d424d4e-ca38-4a06-a28d-7d0ccb1f44cf	\N	f	236e0b55-d417-809b-8a74-d44e81ecdc2d	2025-07-20 12:36:49.35132	\N	\N	\N	\N
